'''鷹嘴珍龜'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Homopus areolatus''）<ref name=Obst>J. Obst, K. Richter, and U. Jacob, ''The Completely Illustrated Atlas of Reptiles and Amphibians for the Terrarium'', [[TFH_Publications|TFH Publications]], 1988.</ref><ref>F. Slavens and K. Slavens, ''Reptiles and Amphibians in Captivity – Breeding, Longevity and Inventory'', 1991.</ref><ref>''The Herpetology Sourcebook'', Reptile & Amphibian Magazine, 1996-1997.</ref>是[[珍龜屬|珍龜屬]]下的一個[[種|種]]。

鷹嘴珍龜原生於[[南非|南非]][[開普省|開普省]]，前足只有四個腳趾，雄性的鼻部在繁殖季節會變成紅色或橘色。因為個頭很小所以極易被捕食，同時由於棲息地破壞及[[偷獵|偷獵]]的緣故，其數量在不斷減少。<ref name=Obst/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.biodiversity.org.na/scripts/taxondisplay.php?taxonlevel=Species&taxonnr=11191 |title=Biodiversity.org |accessdate=2013-08-13 |archive-date=2019-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215070842/http://www.biodiversity.org.na/scripts/taxondisplay.php?taxonlevel=Species&taxonnr=11191 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://membres.multimania.fr/testudo/homopusareolatus.html Membres.multimania.fr] {{Wayback|url=http://membres.multimania.fr/testudo/homopusareolatus.html |date=20100325101952 }} (Retrieved March 17, 2010).</ref>

